OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with mainly light rain, but
OL,8,Fthis will turn heavier and more
OL,9,Fpersistent at time after midnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FCloudy with rain across the
OL,12,FCentral Belt and Argyll, this turning
OL,13,Flight and patchy in the afternoon.
OL,14,FMainly dry and cloudy in the south.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,17,Flargely cloudy and breezy few days
OL,18,Fwith spells of rain, heavy and
OL,19,Fpersistent at times. A few drier
OL,20,Fperiods at times.
